ABOUT.MESSAGE:
'Ello there :wave:, Im Titanbot! Im an open source discord bot library written in C# by Titansmasher, with a fair bit of help from Mildan too!.
This is unfortunately just my base functionality, however there are other bots that run using this bot as its core library.
If you wish to use this library to make your own bot, feel free to do so! You can find me on github here: <https://github.com/Titansmasher/TitanBot>

_If you are seeing this on a fully fledged bot, please contact the owner of said bot because they appear to have not supplied their own about message_

GUILD.TITANLORD:
There are several format strings you can use to have live data in your message.
Use `%USER%` to include the user who started the timer
Use `%TIME%` to include how long until the titan lord is up
Use `%ROUND%` for the round number
Use `%CQ%` for the current CQ number
Use `%COMPLETE%` for the time the titan lord will be up (UTC time)
Alternatively `%COMPLETE+timezone%` can be used to define the timezone, e.g. `%COMPLETE+6%`, minus can also be used but timezone has to be a number from 0 to 12
